node.text:
Hello, hello! Tara silipin nyo ang aking usual activities during my lock in film shooting (nako ma-aatat kayo for sure)! Tsaka syempre para safe, I have all my essentials with me dito sa set. Para naman iwas bagot, I have my #OPPOA94 for games and my mini vlogging sesh! @oppophilippines is perfect for gaming because its special features such as the Bullet Screen Message, Gamer Mode, Gaming Shortcut Mode and Adjustable Gaming Touch, sobrang sarap maglaro sa set kasi di talaga ako nagugulo! Ayos din talaga for vlogging kasi it has Dual-View Video and AI Color Portrait video features para no edit needed videos mo post nalang agad! #LifeLiveAtFullSpeed ka talaga sa smartphone na ito, hindi marunong mapagod!

Itong OPPO A94 is now available in the Philippines and via Shopee-pee-pee-pee for only PHP13,999! Sobrang mura na ito sa dami ng bigatin features, ewan ko nalang talaga kung may ipaglalaban pa kayo dyan!!! Check nyo nalang IG ni @OPPOPhilippines para tapos ang usapan.

node.text: I am the proudest daughter! Within 24 hrs ng wala pa sila video meron na sila silver play button! 😆👏🏼 Now they have 230k+ subs!!! Ang galing nyo mga ka-maintenance! Sobra masaya sila at tutok and basa sa comments nyo. Ibigay na natin sa mga tanders! Follow and watch nyo na sila 😂 #LinkinmyBio
